{"tid":1818250,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解火警鐘測試時正常,就代表真實火警可以正常運作?","createTime":"2020-01-09T17:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T07:15:35.000Z","uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f924003ff904d8455793d97c687fef1c5a954d0c","tid":1818250,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:52:33.000Z","msg":"即係咁<br />\n火警鐘測試時運作正常,我最多只係證明到測試時識響<br />\n但我證明當真係有火警時,個鐘可以正常運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f58d8ffc58ae5ddc9baf827eaec4ddc19626a7","tid":1818250,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:56:58.000Z","msg":"純粹係希望唔會未火燭已經唔work"},{"pid":"90b3e496c18854a5cbcb5f7482e2c60bab0795eb","tid":1818250,"uid":126366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:58:26.000Z","msg":"冇㗎啦<br />\n即係凡事點都有風險嫁啦<br />\n唔通真係燒着嗰個地方再去測試咩"},{"pid":"a0bec350afc068bcfc5ede4c24d3a3e8a7445432","tid":1818250,"uid":131188,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:03:13.000Z","msg":"薛丁格隻貓? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fa258d9dd309b36b7a1cc6a22ca341df3e7e3c","tid":1818250,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:16:54.000Z","msg":"又或者果d汽車安全氣囊<br />\n測試果架撞車時識彈<br />\n但如果我唔拎架自己車去撞一次我點知到時真係識彈出黎<br />\n但我果架撞完我就要渣第二架<br />\n即係我永遠證明唔到而家渣緊果架冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de4bdb718de7784a73c6f6bfece1e34d3b04b24","tid":1818250,"uid":197393,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:19:41.000Z","msg":"邊有人話火警鐘測試正常=正常運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n測試就係試下佢有冇問題，減低佢壞嘅機會咋嘛<br />\n<br />\n滅火筒測試時正常，唔代表真實火警可以正常運作<br />\n咁唔使放滅火筒啦？"},{"pid":"7b8c40c4b47c4aedd0b6ea0c855c83de64c2e388","tid":1818250,"uid":131188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:21:24.000Z","msg":"跳降落傘都係同一原理<br />\n你要用嗰