30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"377bbd509f3479b9a5eef7f067be70f2848574d6","tid":1818250,"uid":131323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T20:14:51.000Z","msg":"你老母大肚果陣照超聲波醫生話冇事<br />\n點知出到黎原來係個弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:50:34.000Z","msg":"弱智好似冇得做產前檢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76048266eba61dac2ded36c110a722a435afd28","tid":1818250,"uid":295602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"有啲野未發生你觀察唔到<br />\n所以只可以做相反嘅野去推測<br />\n做&quot;火警鐘測試&quot;唔係去試&quot;當有火警嗰陣佢會work&quot;<br />\n而係去睇&quot;當我做驗查嗰陣佢會唔會唔work&quot;<br />\n<br />\n好似計probability明明想知P(A)但係會走去計1-P(B)"},{"pid":"4b3788a06f13f6eb68e8d692721292903c38a684","tid":1818250,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9eddec97397208430ec83481d6768ada1f631c57","tid":1818250,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"377bbd509f3479b9a5eef7f067be70f2848574d6","tid":1818250,"uid":131323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T20:14:51.000Z","msg":"你老母大肚果陣照超聲波醫生話冇事<br />\n點知出到黎原來係個弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:50:34.000Z","msg":"弱智好似冇得做產前檢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:58:34.000Z","msg":"有得驗血架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n檢查不嬲都係預防/減少意外發生<br />\n唔保證一定work"},{"pid":"20d64e8b2d3779a588be499c36fe85654da09693","tid":1818250,"uid":297672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:59:14.000Z","msg":"唔可以話保證100%正常，但起碼可以排除部分故障因素。假設當事故發生時，火警鐘會有以下機率分佈：<br />\n<br />\n2%故障（因可排除因素）<br />\n3%故障（因不可排除因素）<br />\n95%正常<br />\n<br />\n未做檢查，故障率係5%<br />\n做過檢查，故障率係3/(3+95)=3.06%<br />\n<br />\n減低咗故障率。"}]}